<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近<delay20 />迷上了畫畫呢。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要有紙和筆，
不管在哪裡都能作畫，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是畫畫最棒的一點呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藉由繪畫不斷表現出自己的想法，<delay20 />
就是我現在的生活意義喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<tag a="110" b="0" />我是最近才開始畫畫的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay40 />我覺得畫畫這種行為，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像是讓自己的心去旅行一樣。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更是一面時常映照出自我的鏡子呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我剛才的說法<delay20 />
是不是很像個藝術家呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正打算<delay8 />
畫一幅油畫大作呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了完成只有我才畫得出來的作品，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每天都一筆一畫慢慢地畫著。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />雖然距離完成好像還要很久，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay8 />不管遇到什麼煩惱，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要泡個暖和的熱水澡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所有煩惱都會一掃而空喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />泡完澡後全身都暖呼呼的，<delay20 />
感覺連心裡的不愉快
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都一起被熱水洗乾淨了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />泡澡不但能洗淨身體，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還能洗滌心靈，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太神奇了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />泡完澡後來杯<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />，
感覺特別好喝呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣一手插腰，然後一口氣喝完，<delay8 />
連煩惱也會忘得一乾二淨喔！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次你也試試看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />用一般的浴缸泡澡可能無法體會，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是用按摩浴缸泡澡，
真的是舒服得就像置身天堂一樣喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整個人泡在浴缸裡，被蓬鬆的泡沫包圍，<delay20 />
好像心裡那一點煩惱之類的，
也全都無所謂了呢，<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="67 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近迷上了做陶藝呢。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="103_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要專心捏著陶土，<delay20 />
就會讓人感覺內心平靜呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為剛開始要做出容器滿困難的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就先從自由創作開始了。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />
你覺得很像在玩黏土？<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才不是呢！<delay20 />是做、<delay8 />陶、<delay8 />藝、<delay8 />啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />長時間和陶土相處，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會開始對著陶土說話呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像面對著<delay8 />
另一個自己一樣。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我剛才的說法<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是很像個藝術家呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正在做<delay20 />
用來插花的花瓶喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />總是做不出
覺得滿意的作品呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為花瓶的形狀<delay8 />太奇特又太搶眼，<delay20 />
反而搶走了花朵身為主角的風采……<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我的功夫還不到家呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="68 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />正在思考<delay20 />
打招呼的重要性呢。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="104_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">看到別人很有精神地跟你打招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是會很開心嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是又常常會覺得不好意思，<delay20 />
最後只敢很小聲的問候回去對吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以每天早上都很有精神地<delay8 />
跟島上的大家打招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是我現在的目標喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「早安！」<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「午安！」<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「晚安！」<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使沒事也可以主動和別人打招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想和誰變熟，這麼做也很有用喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想<delay8 />沒有任何話語比打招呼<delay20 />
更像神奇的魔法咒語了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然每天都會遇到很多不同的事，<delay20 />
但是只有打招呼<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是從來不會變的對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這一定是因為打招呼<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是很重要的事吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是有點憂鬱的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是聽到朋友一聲開朗的問候，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會覺得自己被拯救了一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="69 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a">其實<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay20 />假日都會去當志工喔。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="105_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最喜歡的地方就是
<tag a="110" b="33" />了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我也開始幫花兒澆水，
做些我自己也辦得到的小事了喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣為了誰而努力的感覺，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很棒呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />其實這也不是什麼<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />需要到處宣揚的事情<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我打算偷偷把雜草除乾淨，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />替<tag a="110" b="33" />
進行美化活動喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然聽起來可能有點誇張，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我相信總有一天，<delay8 />
這些小事也能為很多人帶來笑容，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過其實也只是幫忙把遺失物<delay20 />
送還給失主這樣的小事而已。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你也撿到了別人掉的東西，<delay20 />
就去找出失主將東西還回去吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然幫助別人時會有點害羞，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是失主找回東西，
一定會很高興的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="020_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子，<delay8 />
我的時裝街拍<delay8 />被刊登出來了喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是島上的大家看到了，<delay20 />
會不會傳出謠言，<delay8 />
說我一副裝作模特兒的樣子呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你問刊登在那裡？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我老家的免費刊物上啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的朋友間<delay20 />好像流傳著這樣的謠言，<delay8 />
說我厭倦了現代社會，<delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以才在無人島上過著自給自足的生活<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="33" />的生活對我來說，<delay20 />
的確非常療癒沒錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過為什麼謠言會傳成那樣呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="16 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />你聽我說！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前看了一部非常棒的電影喔！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="022_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />離別時將<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />交給對方的
表情和肢體細節表現真的太棒了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也要將它學起來～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />目標成為<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />頂尖選手的主角，<delay8 />
那如專業人士般的動作真的很厲害<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我被演員的敬業精神給感動了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有個場景描述失去意識的主角，<delay20 />
被剛做好的<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的香味喚醒。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看到那就忍不住嚎啕大哭了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="18 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我為了獲得<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />創意方面的刺激，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以有培養參加函授課程的興趣喔。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="024_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我參加的課程是<delay8 />「黏土藝術」喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前有把用黏土做的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /><delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裝飾在房間裡面<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是每個來我家玩的人，<delay8 />
都想把作品吃掉，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我每次都要重新說明，真的很累。
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太有才能也是一件<delay20 />
麻煩的事情呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我參加的課程是<delay8 />「木雕藝術」喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後啊，<delay8 />我前幾天做了個<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="15" />的擺飾。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然都說作品會像它的作者，<delay20 />
但是沒想到我會做得這麼像。<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也因為這樣，<delay8 />我很中意那個擺飾<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透過這件作品，<delay20 /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我窺視到了些許潛藏在<delay8 />
自我當中自戀的一面呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我參加的課程是<delay8 />「手工貼鑽」喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前幾天<delay20 />我把自己愛用的<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
用水鑽好好裝飾了一番喔。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然完成後的作品十分美麗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是因為使用的水鑽太大顆，<delay8 />
所以反而<delay8 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好用在原本的用途上了。
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要兼具實用性和美感，<delay8 />還真是困難呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透過這經驗，我又學到了一件事，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="1a 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看看……<delay20 />現在是<tag a="90" b="33" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經這個時間了！？</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x1b 0x1b 0x1c 0x1d 0x1e 0x1f" /></message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我總覺得才剛剛起床而已，<delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間過得還真快呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白天的紫外線可不容小看，<delay8 />
得好好塗上防曬油才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難怪我覺得早上才剛化完妝不久，<delay8 />
怎麼就已經開始脫妝了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間過得還真是快呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />我得趕快補妝才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="5" />咕嚕<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><colour id="65535" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎、<delay20 />哎呀！<delay20 />抱歉！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難怪我覺得才剛吃完午餐不久，<delay8 />
怎麼肚子就已經開始不安分了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間過得還真是快呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難怪我覺得中午才剛補完妝不久，<delay20 />
怎麼皮膚就開始失去光澤了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間過得還真是快呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我希望自己在晚上看起來也能閃亮動人，<delay8 />
好想幫肌膚添加點光澤啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來得重新補上底妝才行呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正覺得一天才剛要開始，<delay8 />
沒想到就已經要結束了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間過得還真是快呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" />討厭啦！
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我還沒做晚上的肌膚保養！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />睡前敷面膜可是必不可少的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>